parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Valid values: **1** to **50**. Default value: **50**.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results. Valid values:

*   If this is your first request and no next requests are to be performed, you do not need to specify this parameter.
*   If a next request is to be performed, set the value to the value of **NextToken** that is returned from the last call.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description:
The region ID of the endpoint.

You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~DescribeRegions~~) operation to query the most recent region list.

parameters.name: ServiceId
parameters.description: The ID of the endpoint service that you want to query.

parameters.name: ServiceName
parameters.description: The name of the endpoint service that you want to query.

parameters.name: ServiceType
parameters.description:
The type of the endpoint service.

Set the value to **Interface**. You can specify CLB and ALB instances as service resources for the endpoint service.
